Contemporary two level commercial office set around a central atrium area that provides abundant natural light throughout and outstanding staff amenity.

Part or whole building offering via sub lease until June 2023, or longer via direct lease.

Located on the border of Subiaco, this building is in proximity to an abundance of retail and public transport amenity.

The building has been refurbished throughout to provide high quality office accommodation with a combination of meeting rooms, offices, open plan workstations and kitchen/breakout areas.

Flexible offerings from 1000 - 1400sqm

High parking ratio available.

For any queries, please contact the exclusive leasing agents.

Modern partitioned office space available to lease at 516 Hay Street, one of Subiaco's premier office buildings.

The building is well located in the heart of the 'Subi Centro' precinct within close proximity to the Subiaco train station and many cafes and food & beverage options.


The following areas are currently available:

Ground floor: 490sqm. Refurbished open plan space with high ceilings.

Level 1: 1,750sqm (can be split from approx 750sqm) Partitioned whole floor tenancy including reception, board room, 8 meeting rooms, 3 quiet rooms, storage / utility areas, 177 work stations, kitchen / breakout area with direct access into an exclusive courtyard / bbq area of 136sqm. 

Level 2: 752sqm. Refurbished open plan space. 

The building also features:

- Newly refurbished 'end of trip' facilities
- Secure Car Parking 
- Store Rooms
- Signage Rights
- Delivery dock.

Recognized as one of the best office buildings in Subiaco, 437 Roberts Road provides high quality office accommodation over 3 levels, two levels of secure basement car parking plus 'end of trip' facilities and store rooms.

The building occupies a premium Subiaco address on the corner of Roberts Road and Agnew Way in close proximity to the Subiaco train station and the many retail / F&B options in the area.

Level 1, 736 (can be split from approx 300sqm or expanded up to 796sqm): high quality fitout including a large reception area, two board rooms that link together, 2 meeting rooms, 45 work stations (ability to install more), server room and kitchen / breakout area. 

Prominent signage rights available.

High car bay allocation of 1 bay per 32sqm (more available by negotiation).

For further details or to arrange an inspection please contact Luke Bray 0403 184 340 or Luke.Bray@cbre.com.au

54 Salvado Road, Wembley - 

Prominent two level office building with secure basement car parking, occupying a high exposure location on the corner of Salvado Road and Harborne Street.

Building signage rights available!

The building is located on the border of Wembley and Subiaco, within walking distance to Subiaco Train Station, St John of God Hospital and excellent retail amenity. 

NABERS Rating - 4.0 Stars.

Partitioned or open plan office accommodation available 

The side-core configuration of the building provides for functional floor plates, excellent natural light and self-contained amenities.

This tenancy is currently partitioned with a high number of offices and meeting facilities, however the owner can alter the fitout.

Level 1 - 681 sqm

Partitioned or open plan tenancy which currently incorporates a high number of perimeter offices, internal meeting rooms, kitchen and bathroom facilities.

EOT facilities including showers and bicycle parking.

Outgoings - Payable by the Lessee and currently estimated at $155.82/sqm.

High parking ratio of 1 bay per 47sqm
